{\pard\sl-108\slmult0\par

{\pard\plain \li0\sl299\slmult1 \ri360\nooverflow\ql\fi480 {\f1\fs20 An even more noxious, yet similarly futile law has been enacted in California. Since this is bound to be the model for similar laws enacted throughout the country, let's examine it more closely.}\par}
