{\pard\sl-80\slmult0\par

{\pard\plain \li0\sl275\slmult1 \ri0\nooverflow\ql\fi480 {\f1\fs19 The reasons for the popularity of this method are twofold. Firstly, this method does not require the use of methylamine because the methylamino group is already incorporated in the ephedrine molecule. Secondly, ephedrine is still easily available. It is much more easily obtained than phenylacetic acid. This may change in the future, but at present an underground chemist can buy 1000-lot quantities of stimulant pills (containing 25 milligrams of ephedrine) by mail at very reasonable prices.}\par}
