{\pard\plain \li0\sl279\slmult1 \ri360\nooverflow\qj\fi480 {\f1\fs20 These methods all have the advantage of being quick and simple, but they also have their unique disadvantages, along with the general shared disadvantage that the starting material must be gathered bits at a time from bottles of pills.}\par}
