{\pard\plain \li0\sl269\slmult1 \ri0\nooverflow\ql\fi480 {\f1\fs20 Next the filtered batch is poured into a 1000 ml round bottom flask, a few boiling chips are added, and the glassware is set up for refluxing. Plastic tubing is attached to the top of the condenser and led outside. The mixture is boiled under reflux for one hour to force out the excess ammonia.}\par}
